{"type":"text","timestamp":1775883283933,"sessionID":"ses_28521088effewq5bKneqHzbGUF","part":{"id":"prt_d7ae44b260010T2nW4yWu9aXP6","messageID":"msg_d7ae43f16001a3Rwt2mveRcJ4T","sessionID":"ses_28521088effewq5bKneqHzbGUF","type":"text","text":"I've implemented comprehensive unit tests for the agentcube Go project:\n\n## Summary of Tests Written\n\n### 1. Store Package (`pkg/store/store_test.go`)\n- `TestStoreInterface` - Full interface testing including:\n  - Ping\n  - StoreSandbox (nil, zero expiry, empty sessionID, success cases)\n  - GetSandboxBySessionID (found, not found)\n  - UpdateSandbox (nil, empty session, not found, success)\n  - DeleteSandboxBySessionID\n  - ListExpiredSandboxes (zero/negative limit, success, limit)\n  - ListInactiveSandboxes (success, empty)\n  - UpdateSessionLastActivity (empty, not found, success)\n  - Close\n- `TestStoreSandboxWithEntryPoints` - Tests storing sandboxes with entry points\n- `TestMultipleSessions` - Tests storing and retrieving multiple sessions\n\n### 2. PicoD Package (`pkg/picod/auth_manager_test.go`)\n- `TestAuthManager_NewAuthManager`\n- `TestAuthManager_GetPublicKey`\n- `TestAuthManager_LoadPublicKeyFromEnv_Empty`\n- `TestAuthManager_ReloadPublicKey`\n- `TestAuthManager_Middleware_*` - Multiple middleware tests (missing header, invalid format, no key, valid token, expired token, invalid token)\n- `TestAuthManager_RequireAuth`\n- `TestAuthErrorCodes`\n- `TestMaxBodySize`\n- `TestLoadRSAPublicKey_*` - Tests for loading RSA public keys\n\n### 3. Router Package (`pkg/router/proxy_route_test.go`)\n- `TestNewProxy`\n- `TestProxy_GetTransport`\n- `TestProxy_ServeHTTP_NilBackend`\n- `TestProxy_ServeHTTP_Overloaded`\n- `TestNewRouteHandler`\n- `TestRouteHandler_GetBackendForRequest_ByHeader`\n- `TestRouteHandler_GetBackendForRequest_ByPath`\n- `TestRouteHandler_GetBackendForRequest_NotFound`\n- `TestRouteHandler_ServeHTTP_WithBackend`\n\n## Test Results\n- **picod tests**: All 47 tests pass ✓\n- **router tests**: My new tests pass; pre-existing test failures exist (prometheus metrics re-registration, test logic issues)\n- **store tests**: Cannot compile due to pre-existing API mismatch in `store_valkey.go` (the valkey-go library version v1.0.73 has a different API than used in the code)","time":{"start":1775883283930,"end":1775883283930}}}
